Packages 
Package Description
edu.gatech.cs2340.trydent
All general-purpose game engine objects which most games will need.
edu.gatech.cs2340.trydent.animation
Classes pertaining to animating the motion of game objects.
edu.gatech.cs2340.trydent.internal
Internal engine classes users should never need to look at.
edu.gatech.cs2340.trydent.log
Message logging utilities.
edu.gatech.cs2340.trydent.math
Mathematics, geometry, linear algebra.
edu.gatech.cs2340.trydent.math.curve
Classes to express geometric curves of various sizes and shapes, including timing and interpolations.
edu.gatech.cs2340.trydent.sample
Sample classes demonstrating engine functionality and use.
edu.gatech.cs2340.trydent.sample.tictactoe
Example of a simple tic-tac-toe game using the Trydent game engine.
